name: TrumpvsBiden
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: trump versus biden
des:
Ready to challenge Biden or Obama? With "Morgan vs Bugo" you can choose your favorite character and give life to a great challenge!
You are Trump, Biden is your opponent and with 3 shots at your disposal you have to challenge and beat him! But you can also challenge other characters, just say "Play with" followed by the name of your favorite character to challenge him. Whenever you choose a character, a fantastic animated image will be shown on your Echo Show and you will hear its audio!
Have you chosen Obama? Hit and by magic you will see one of the most beautiful images of Obama appear on your screen! Have you chosen Hilary Clinton? Hear it in the remix that caused such a stir!

The characters at your disposal are:
- Barak Obama
- Joe Biden
- Hilary Clinton
- Richard Nixon

If you have a favorite character and want to add them, please leave a review with their name and we'll add them soon!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
